+// kfactory: read the access token from the shared launcher cache when
+// no explicit bearer / env var is provided. Single source of truth is
+// `~/.config/kfactory/auth.json` (path passed via
+// OPENCODE_SERVER_BEARER_CACHE_PATH). Catches the case where kfactory
